0:02:25.900,0:02:28.880
Consort Fleur, what is the matter with you?

0:02:29.160,0:02:32.400
Why would you spoil the mood on such a joyous day?

0:02:36.026,0:02:38.060
It's not that I harbor grievances against anyone.

0:02:39.206,0:02:42.240
Seeing Lady Sourire perform "Dance of the Startled Swan"

0:02:42.685,0:02:45.800
deeply touched me in my heart of hearts,
and I slipped on decorum.

0:02:46.906,0:02:51.700
You had not entered the family
when Empress Première performed the "Startled Swan."

0:02:52.389,0:02:55.880
Why are you emotional about the dance today?

0:02:56.640,0:02:59.601
I've been idling away my days reading poetry,

0:02:59.827,0:03:03.559
I stumbled upon "Lament from the East Tower" by Consort Mei.

0:03:04.326,0:03:06.575
Her poem filled me with dread.

0:03:07.120,0:03:11.200
Consort Mei composed "Dance of the Startled Swan" 
when she was in high favor with Emperor Xuanzong.

0:03:12.577,0:03:16.421
She wrote this poem during the time she was confined to Shangyang Palace.

0:03:17.266,0:03:20.959
The "Startled Swan" today brought my mind to her "Lament from the East Tower."

0:03:21.716,0:03:25.003
I can't refrain from feeling sad for Consort Mei.

0:03:26.349,0:03:29.720
You've never shown much interest in poetry before.

0:03:30.463,0:03:32.583
Why have you become fond of reading poems?

0:03:32.788,0:03:37.526
I heard that poetry and literature can enlighten untutored minds.

0:03:38.427,0:03:40.142
Devoid of talent and virtue,

0:03:40.289,0:03:45.160
I will not have the face to serve Your Majesty
if I don't cultivate my character.

0:03:45.427,0:03:49.050
Since you sympathize with the poem,

0:03:50.080,0:03:51.825
why not share your thoughts with us?

0:03:55.369,0:04:00.940
“Your fond words said
your love would bind us inseparably.”

0:04:01.000,0:04:06.623
"It’ll endure as the sun and the moon," you vowed,
"it’ll abide as mountains and seas."

0:04:07.400,0:04:11.840
“How she [Yang Guifei, another consort]
seethed with wrathful jealousy.”

0:04:12.285,0:04:17.070
“She deprived me of your love,
banishing me into this forlorn tower.”

0:04:18.278,0:04:24.476
“No more can I reach the bliss of yesteryears;
in dreams, I see only a hazy memory.”

0:04:26.353,0:04:28.462
Every time I read these lines,

0:04:28.773,0:04:32.077
I am deeply saddened by Consort Mei's
love and longing for her husband.

0:04:41.559,0:04:46.580
Your Majesty, the matter concerning Consort Fleur
is a family affair within your harem.

0:04:46.844,0:04:48.744
I dare not comment on it.

0:04:49.103,0:04:54.943
But Her Highness hasn't committed
any serious wrongs while serving Your Majesty all these years.

0:04:55.299,0:04:57.580
If there was something unthoughtful in her service,

0:04:57.580,0:05:02.700
I hope Your Majesty can forgive Her Highness
considering her many years of dedicated service.

0:05:07.667,0:05:08.879
Consort Fleur,

0:05:09.814,0:05:12.451
it must have been hard on you.

0:05:13.330,0:05:15.599
Your residence in the Summer Palace is quite remote.

0:05:16.041,0:05:18.400
I'll visit you more often when I have the time.

0:05:21.901,0:05:24.031
I thank Your Majesty.

0:05:27.291,0:05:29.362
Cao, I am curious to know...

0:05:29.688,0:05:34.392
The slip with "Dance of the Startled Swan" written on it
was hidden in your sleeve, wasn't it?

0:05:36.000,0:05:39.740
So my dance was not destined, but orchestrated to happen.

0:05:40.277,0:05:42.160
I must thank you for the effort.

0:05:42.720,0:05:44.344
Sourire, what are you talking about?

0:05:44.515,0:05:46.495
I do not understand.

0:05:46.833,0:05:48.569
Your acute mind must understand that

0:05:48.758,0:05:52.508
without "Startled Swan," "Lament from the East Tower" 
would not have been written.

0:05:53.415,0:05:57.840
While Consort Mei's heart-rending poem
failed to rekindle the love of Emperor Xuanzong,

0:05:58.302,0:06:00.842
Her Highness Consort Fleur moved His Majesty deeply.

0:06:02.000,0:06:06.560
Consort Mei's unrestful soul
must be so appreciative of your painstaking effort.

0:06:07.000,0:06:10.340
It is whatever you say, Sourire.

0:06:11.000,0:06:14.100
My tongue lacks the eloquence to vindicate myself.

0:06:14.280,0:06:18.880
Perhaps you should spend all your free time
taking care of Lady Vertu's pregnancy.

0:06:19.000,0:06:21.700
After all, that's His Majesty's prime concern.

0:06:21.860,0:06:23.300
By all means.

0:06:35.920,0:06:40.820
We exerted so much effort trying to bring her down,
only to watch her rise up again.

0:06:41.000,0:06:43.260
I can't accept this!

0:06:43.400,0:06:47.680
Meizhuang, you know this. 
Her rising is expected.

0:06:48.000,0:06:49.800
It's always just a matter of time.

0:06:50.433,0:06:53.000
I'm just afraid that our life will become difficult again.

0:06:53.920,0:06:57.400
With this sweetheart in your belly,
there's nothing we should worry about.

0:06:57.800,0:07:01.300
Don't let anything upset you. 
Your pregnancy matters the most.

0:07:01.400,0:07:04.680
It's only been one month.
We don't even know if it's a boy or a girl.

0:07:04.720,0:07:07.734
Regardless, they will always be our dearest baby.

0:07:08.584,0:07:12.840
Dear baby, please tell your mother to stop feeling upset.

0:07:14.555,0:07:16.375
Stop talking nonsense.

0:07:17.344,0:07:20.522
What happened today will be more of a headache
to the Empress than to us.

0:07:20.860,0:07:23.320
Let's not fret when Her Majesty doesn't.

0:07:24.120,0:07:25.700
You are right.

0:07:26.242,0:07:29.433
But I couldn't help feeling worried when you were dancing.

0:07:29.840,0:07:31.611
I knew that you could dance well.

0:07:31.611,0:07:35.035
But I never expected it would be an offense
either way - dancing, or not.

0:07:35.520,0:07:37.240
I got by with sheer luck.

0:07:38.020,0:07:41.240
But we can never be too careful given
Lady Cao's deep cunning and guile.

0:07:42.000,0:07:45.060
No matter how she tried to harm you,
you are shielded by His Majesty's favor.

0:07:45.900,0:07:48.427
But why were you hiding your talents from His Majesty?

0:07:48.783,0:07:52.540
If she had seen your skills beforehand,
she wouldn't have plotted this against you.

0:07:52.600,0:07:55.300
Fortunately, they are not aware of my strengths and shortcomings.

0:07:55.400,0:07:57.920
Otherwise, they would be even bolder in their plots.

0:08:03.022,0:08:07.800
Lady Sourire, His Majesty invites you to appreciate
his newly collected poems at the Governance Hall.

0:08:08.600,0:08:11.187
Go immediately. Don't make His Majesty wait.

0:08:12.080,0:08:13.320
I'll go now.

0:08:21.526,0:08:22.582
Mr Su.

0:08:22.582,0:08:24.226
Peace to Lady Sourire.

0:08:25.004,0:08:27.301
His Majesty is currently in a meeting with some officials.

0:08:27.524,0:08:29.657
I hope you won't mind waiting here for a while, My Lady.

0:08:30.260,0:08:31.191
Certainly.

0:08:32.295,0:08:35.755
Your Majesty, considering the ongoing wars in the northwest,

0:08:36.300,0:08:39.400
the service of Consort Fleur's brother
Nian Gengyao is crucial to the state.

0:08:40.000,0:08:41.640
I hope Your Majesty will reconsider.

0:08:42.500,0:08:46.360
At this juncture, a decision regarding court appointments should be expedient.

0:08:46.360,0:08:49.980
Your Majesty's forgiveness of Consort Fleur
will also lift military morale.

0:08:50.453,0:08:53.156
I understand. You can leave now.

0:08:57.340,0:08:59.040
Peace to My Lady.

0:09:02.400,0:09:04.040
My Lady, please.

0:09:07.641,0:09:09.712
Your Majesty, Lady Sourire is here.

0:09:13.000,0:09:16.020
I bow before Your Majesty.
Peace and grace to Your Majesty.

0:09:16.599,0:09:20.119
I have a headache. I can use a massage from you.

0:09:21.010,0:09:22.200
Yes.

0:09:39.100,0:09:40.960
Is something troubling Your Majesty?

0:09:41.450,0:09:43.080
How do you know?

0:09:45.320,0:09:50.780
Despite jasmine flowers being placed in the chamber,
I can still detect the scent of menthol.

0:09:52.240,0:09:55.740
I know Your Majesty applies menthol
when something is bothering you.

0:09:56.760,0:09:58.949
You are always attentive to my mind.

0:10:02.880,0:10:07.080
Take a guess at what is bothering me.

0:10:08.338,0:10:12.258
Your Majesty is concerned with everything under Heaven.
It must be some trouble at court.

0:10:14.640,0:10:15.956
You are not wrong.

0:10:16.220,0:10:20.560
But the harem falls under Heaven as well,
and it too gives me trouble.

0:10:22.396,0:10:27.064
It has been hard on Her Majesty the Empress
to single-handedly manage all the affairs in the harem.

0:10:27.390,0:10:29.320
It is time someone share her burden.

0:10:30.260,0:10:31.800
What do you think?

0:10:32.440,0:10:36.380
Consort Fleur has always assisted
Her Majesty with palace affairs.

0:10:37.149,0:10:40.109
Whatever happened was the mistake of Concubine Beauté.

0:10:40.599,0:10:42.859
Consort Fleur was not necessarily involved.

0:10:43.700,0:10:48.040
Her Majesty the Empress Dowager was just dissatisfied
 over Consort Fleur being a little overbearing.

0:10:48.653,0:10:50.707
I believe Her Highness has learned a lesson.

0:10:56.000,0:11:00.540
But Consort Fleur....
That will make you feel aggrieved.

0:11:02.040,0:11:05.538
But don't worry, I'll protect you from any harm.

0:11:09.180,0:11:13.860
I will never feel aggrieved over anything
 if it's for Your Majesty.

0:11:20.100,0:11:23.960
What a rare day today!
Even State Prince Dun spoke up for Your Highness.

0:11:24.377,0:11:28.597
He has always been a haughty man,
not even respectful towards His Majesty.

0:11:29.224,0:11:31.360
He's entitled to feel superior.

0:11:32.540,0:11:36.440
His mother, Noble Consort Wenxi,
is the younger sister of Empress Xiaozhaoren,

0:11:37.100,0:11:41.580
while the current Empress Dowager was merely
 preceptor maid to Empress Xiaozhaoren.

0:11:41.580,0:11:43.839
After the battle for the throne among the nine lords,

0:11:43.839,0:11:47.880
although State Prince Dun's associates
Lords VIII,  IV, and XIV were banished,

0:11:48.476,0:11:50.956
he managed to retain the title of State Prince.

0:11:52.781,0:11:56.680
But he cannot swallow his anger 
over His Majesty's rise to the throne.

0:11:57.820,0:11:59.717
Then why would he help Your Highness?

0:12:00.804,0:12:03.500
He was not helping me.

0:12:03.640,0:12:07.440
He was "pushing the boat along the current" 
to earn favor from my brother.

0:12:07.440,0:12:08.880
Great General Nian?

0:12:08.922,0:12:17.100
Prince Dun was highly ranked among his brothers
and worked with my brother on affairs in Qinghai Province.

0:12:17.280,0:12:19.180
Perhaps he did it for old times' sake.

0:12:23.665,0:12:29.760
For whatever reason, I'm happy as long as
 Your Highness regains His Majesty's favor.

0:12:32.740,0:12:34.160
Is the dress ready?

0:12:34.200,0:12:35.640
It is, Your Highness.

0:12:35.640,0:12:38.060
His Majesty likes seeing Your Highness in red.

0:12:39.600,0:12:42.000
- Then hurry and help me get changed.
- Yes, Your Highness.

0:12:42.100,0:12:43.500
I must not make His Majesty wait.

0:12:48.500,0:12:51.180
Your Majesty had a long day.
You should rest early.

0:12:52.191,0:12:55.080
All the smiling I put on today
has made my face sore.

0:12:56.009,0:12:59.460
On such an occasion, Your Majesty had to
wear a smile regardless of your feelings.

0:12:59.800,0:13:01.180
It must be hard on Your Majesty.

0:13:01.500,0:13:05.440
But an empress must never say she's tired.

0:13:06.899,0:13:10.356
If those who covet my throne ever find 
my power weaker than my will,

0:13:10.959,0:13:14.578
they will "skin and eat me alive".

0:13:15.960,0:13:17.200
Your Majesty is right.

0:13:17.889,0:13:21.111
Consort Fleur today... what a small woman to have gotten her way.

0:13:21.111,0:13:23.111
It disgusted me.

0:13:23.200,0:13:26.160
But she did not disgust His Majesty.

0:13:28.140,0:13:36.180
Only, I couldn't help thinking of my son Honghui,
on the ceremony of his first birthday.

0:13:36.900,0:13:39.180
If the First Prince were still with us ...

0:13:39.680,0:13:41.698
If Honghui were with us,

0:13:42.100,0:13:45.033
he would have grown taller than the Third Prince,

0:13:45.033,0:13:47.080
and more handsome.

0:13:47.316,0:13:49.225
And much smarter than the Third Prince.

0:13:51.920,0:13:53.475
Indeed.

0:13:53.852,0:13:57.117
Honghui began to read characters
when he was only two years old.

0:13:58.500,0:14:00.829
The Third Prince has nothing that compares.

0:14:02.400,0:14:06.040
Your Majesty is in your prime.
You will certainly have one more prince.

0:14:07.500,0:14:12.540
I'm past forty years of age,
not suitable for pregnancy anymore.

0:14:13.789,0:14:18.169
And after my sister died, 
His Majesty never treated me the same way.

0:14:20.000,0:14:23.240
I know the condition of my health.

0:14:23.240,0:14:25.113
I'm afraid I'll never be able to.

0:14:26.000,0:14:29.920
Even though His Majesty doesn't say so,
he has a lot of respect for Your Majesty in his heart.

0:14:31.100,0:14:38.160
when a woman does not have her husband's love,
what is the use of his respect?

0:14:40.380,0:14:42.980
You've been through all these years with me.

0:14:43.604,0:14:48.500
How do you think His Majesty has treated me
compared to how he treated my sister?

0:14:49.180,0:14:55.360
Your Majesty, before Empress Première entered
the family, His Majesty treated you extremely well.

0:14:59.260,0:15:02.809
His Majesty never treated me
as well as he treated my sister.

0:15:03.911,0:15:05.711
And the Empress Dowager too.

0:15:09.280,0:15:13.280
After all, I am the daughter of a secondary wife
while my sister was of a primary wife.

0:15:15.620,0:15:21.180
If my son Honghui were with us,
he would have been the eldest son and of a primary wife.

0:15:21.906,0:15:24.226
What a distinguished status he would have.

0:15:30.340,0:15:32.685
When Honghui was dying,

0:15:34.360,0:15:37.014
it was raining just like this.

0:15:42.000,0:15:43.446
Autumn,

0:15:44.320,0:15:46.300
my migraine is piercing right now.

0:15:46.920,0:15:48.400
Your Majesty...

0:15:52.000,0:15:53.880
Your Majesty...

