0:16:05.000,0:16:08.940
My Lady, how was your appetite the last two days?
Do you still feel nauseous?

0:16:09.355,0:16:12.949
It's strange.
I haven't felt nauseous lately.

0:16:13.213,0:16:16.660
But my stomach aches and feels cold.
I wonder what the reason is.

0:16:17.202,0:16:22.182
My Lady, you will continue to feel at ease
as you have been taking the prenatal tonics.

0:16:23.180,0:16:25.620
As for the stomach pain...

0:16:26.164,0:16:31.620
it is normal at one month of pregnancy.

0:16:31.800,0:16:33.860
I feel reassured hearing you say that.

0:16:34.226,0:16:38.120
I thought the pregnancy symptoms
would be strong in the first month.

0:16:38.200,0:16:41.200
Nay. You are in good health, My Lady.
You would not have such symptoms.

0:16:41.300,0:16:45.380
I believe you will give birth to a 
healthy prince for His Majesty.

0:16:46.276,0:16:47.829
I hope I fulfill your auspicious words.

0:16:48.643,0:16:50.200
- Lunar.
- Yes.

0:16:50.200,0:16:53.300
Grant Dr. Liu some of the hawthorn cakes my father sent.

0:16:53.300,0:16:54.600
Thank you, My Lady.

0:17:05.000,0:17:09.400
The hawthorn cakes must be
made by Qishunzhai Bakery.

0:17:10.640,0:17:13.940
Qishunzhai was closed the year before last.

0:17:14.091,0:17:18.460
Dr. Liu, you were transferred to the palace this year.
Why didn't you know?

0:17:20.960,0:17:24.720
I always think of Qishunzhai when I miss home.

0:17:24.900,0:17:27.300
It feels as if the bakery should still be there.

0:17:27.300,0:17:29.960
I apologize for my slip of the tongue.

0:17:30.240,0:17:32.340
You must be missing home a lot.

0:17:33.320,0:17:37.100
I will have Lunar send you more if you like.

0:17:37.280,0:17:39.540
I thank My Lady in advance.

0:17:40.240,0:17:41.520
- Poria.
- Yes.

0:17:41.520,0:17:43.920
- See Dr. Liu out.
- Yes.

0:17:43.920,0:17:45.740
This way please, Dr. Liu.

0:17:46.065,0:17:47.745
I bow to thank My Lady.

0:18:05.380,0:18:08.320
Please take a break, My Lady.
Don't strain your eyes.

0:18:15.460,0:18:18.000
This one is almost done.
I will finish it.

0:18:18.000,0:18:19.460
There's no hurry, My Lady.

0:18:19.649,0:18:24.769
Lady Vertu is just one month into her pregnancy.
You have eight more months to finish the bib.

0:18:25.740,0:18:28.000
I must finish this as soon as possible.

0:18:28.400,0:18:32.680
If Meizhuang likes it, I will make a few more.

0:18:34.000,0:18:37.500
You have no idea how fast a baby grows.

0:18:37.900,0:18:40.180
They outgrow their clothes in no time.

0:18:40.400,0:18:43.335
It's not like you've had children of your own.

0:18:48.360,0:18:54.780
Growing up, I watched my mother
do needlework for the concubines' children.

0:18:56.120,0:18:58.140
That is how I have the knowledge.

0:18:58.900,0:19:01.380
I'm sorry to have triggered
your sad memories, My Lady.

0:19:01.380,0:19:02.880
I will take any punishment.

0:19:03.000,0:19:04.480
Please rise.

0:19:05.320,0:19:06.867
Why would I punish you?

0:19:08.000,0:19:11.140
But I wonder how my mother has been.

0:19:11.602,0:19:14.780
She must be so honored
that you have entered the palace.

0:19:15.195,0:19:17.434
I'm just a neglected Companion.

0:19:18.415,0:19:22.020
His Majesty might not even remember who I am.

0:19:25.731,0:19:28.321
The dragon will have to stay where it is

0:19:29.377,0:19:31.200
before having a chance to soar.

0:19:33.774,0:19:35.614
My Lady, terrible news.

0:19:36.439,0:19:37.330
What happened?

0:19:37.330,0:19:38.689
Mr. An had an accident.

0:19:42.620,0:19:43.820
My Lady.

0:19:47.660,0:19:49.140
My sisters.

0:19:50.040,0:19:51.480
My sisters, help me!

0:19:51.480,0:19:53.980
- Longrong, what happened?
- Rise. Take it easy.

0:19:54.000,0:19:56.640
My father is in jail!

0:19:57.100,0:19:59.620
How did that happen all of a sudden?

0:19:59.900,0:20:01.380
I received a letter from home saying

0:20:01.380,0:20:08.000
while my father assisted the magistrate -
Jiang Wenqing - 
transferring army provisions to the Northwest,

0:20:08.700,0:20:13.480
enemy troops attacked them halfway and robbed the provisions.

0:20:14.220,0:20:17.640
Jiang Wenqing escaped and stole lots of money.

0:20:18.700,0:20:24.260
His Majesty, shaking with rage,
decreed my father's arrest along with Jiang Wenqing.

0:20:25.200,0:20:27.820
I don't know if he will live or not.

0:20:28.820,0:20:33.120
Given such fierce anger I'm afraid His Majesty
 will sentence my father to death!

0:20:35.700,0:20:38.860
Did you confirm your father wasn't involved at all?

0:20:38.860,0:20:40.060
I am sure!

0:20:40.060,0:20:43.360
My father has always been cautious in his dealings.

0:20:43.813,0:20:47.000
He would never involve himself in what Jiang Wenqing did.

0:20:48.020,0:20:50.580
Don't cry, Lingrong.
There's no conclusion to this matter yet.

0:20:50.806,0:20:52.380
We must think of a solution.

0:20:52.380,0:20:53.111
Exactly.

0:20:53.111,0:20:57.161
I understand that anything concerning
the military is of great consequence.

0:20:57.840,0:21:02.340
I'm afraid the odds are more ominous than propitious.

0:21:03.041,0:21:06.621
We will definitely try to speak to His Majesty on your behalf.

0:21:07.700,0:21:11.600
It's just that... we are not allowed
to pass comments on state affairs.

0:21:11.700,0:21:12.700
You're right.

0:21:12.820,0:21:14.680
There's no need to disturb His Majesty.

0:21:14.780,0:21:17.660
In fact, Meizhuang can help me.

0:21:17.660,0:21:18.500
Me?

0:21:19.380,0:21:22.320
The incident happened within the jurisdiction of Jizhou.

0:21:22.697,0:21:26.253
Your father, as the region's Commander, 
will be the interrogator.

0:21:28.300,0:21:32.674
- Meizhuang, I beg of you to help my father.
- Please stand.

0:21:32.900,0:21:35.052
I will see what I can do.

0:21:35.580,0:21:37.159
I need to think ...

0:21:38.000,0:21:43.500
Please have mercy on my father.
A letter from you will be enough to save his life.

0:21:43.700,0:21:45.620
Of course, don't worry.

0:21:46.039,0:21:49.839
But I must request an audience with His Majesty
and sound out his opinion.

0:21:52.240,0:21:54.040
Thank you, Meizhuang!

0:21:55.400,0:21:58.556
I'm eternally grateful for your help.

0:22:00.000,0:22:01.560
Lingrong, don't cry.

0:22:10.200,0:22:11.598
Aiyo, Lady Vertu...

0:22:11.787,0:22:13.900
What brought you here carrying the child?

0:22:14.126,0:22:16.000
Be careful not to be affected by the heat.

0:22:16.100,0:22:17.404
Is His Majesty inside?

0:22:17.520,0:22:20.966
Yes, but he's with Zhang Tingyu and General Longkodo.

0:22:21.760,0:22:23.340
I'm afraid you'll have to wait for a while, My Lady.

0:22:23.340,0:22:26.420
Why is General Longkodo here?

0:22:28.100,0:22:31.000
An accident happened to the
army provisions for the Northwest.

0:22:31.100,0:22:34.040
His Majesty is outraged about it.

0:22:34.496,0:22:36.536
Does that involve Companion An's father?

0:22:36.800,0:22:38.536
That, I have no idea.

0:22:39.453,0:22:45.160
All I know is that His Majesty has announced
the head official, Jiang Wenqing to be beheaded immediately.

0:22:45.300,0:22:47.680
What ... what about the other officials?

0:22:47.700,0:22:49.600
I don't know, My Lady.

0:22:49.700,0:22:54.240
So ... you came here for Companion An's father, My Lady?

0:22:54.300,0:22:57.920
Yes, Companion An was overcome with grief.
I have to do something.

0:22:58.220,0:22:59.380
No no no ...

0:22:59.380,0:23:03.920
In my view, My Lady, all you can do is stand by.

0:23:04.814,0:23:06.600
I hope you will enlighten me, sir.

0:23:09.306,0:23:12.320
His Majesty strongly disapproves of
any concubine interfering in state affairs.

0:23:12.500,0:23:17.500
This is a great concern for the military, 
especially for General Nian Gengyao.

0:23:17.600,0:23:21.160
If you speak for Companion An,
isn't that equivalent to offending Consort Fleur?

0:23:21.160,0:23:23.540
But this is not about offending anyone.

0:23:23.766,0:23:27.380
I cannot just stand and watch
when I can save someone's life.

0:23:27.664,0:23:29.920
I'm afraid that is what you will have to do.

0:23:30.000,0:23:33.780
Please consider:  your father will be lenient as soon as he receives a letter from you;

0:23:33.780,0:23:38.080
it makes no difference if His Majesty knows of your involvement or not.

0:23:38.860,0:23:43.340
But if someone uses your action
 in order to provoke anger in His Majesty,

0:23:43.840,0:23:47.540
wouldn't that imperil your father's post?

0:23:51.300,0:23:54.980
But what if Companion An's father is not guilty...?

0:23:55.000,0:23:59.360
If so, he will be proven innocent after investigation.

0:23:59.500,0:24:03.380
You didn't see how furious His Majesty was just now.

0:24:03.719,0:24:07.119
It's not worthwhile to risk His Majesty's favor for this matter.

0:24:07.774,0:24:12.594
Also, you are now with child and in sight of
the power to assist in palace management,

0:24:12.820,0:24:15.780
why would you wade into this muddy water?

0:24:15.900,0:24:20.500
And if Her Highness Consort Fleur
hears about your pleading,

0:24:21.217,0:24:24.536
Companion An's father will definitely die.

0:24:27.500,0:24:28.563
Then ...

0:24:35.000,0:24:38.600
- Sir, please don't tell His Majesty that I came.
- Yes.

0:24:38.700,0:24:41.720
It is hot out here.
Please go quickly, My Lady.

0:24:51.339,0:24:55.379
Don't be sad. We'll think of another way.

0:24:56.200,0:24:58.220
What other way?

0:24:58.980,0:25:00.960
Even Meizhuang wasn't able to do anything about it.

0:25:01.500,0:25:03.580
No one else would be able to.

0:25:03.882,0:25:05.882
What Meizhuang said is reasonable.

0:25:06.000,0:25:10.220
If she speaks up for you, Consort Fleur
will spare no effort to put your father to death.

0:25:11.546,0:25:13.646
But what else can I do?

0:25:13.956,0:25:19.636
His Majesty has announced the
immediate execution of Jiang Wenqing today.

0:25:21.439,0:25:22.901
Tomorrow ...

0:25:23.343,0:25:26.022
it could be my father.

0:25:29.295,0:25:31.071
Let's go see the Empress.

0:25:32.602,0:25:33.602
The Empress ...

0:25:39.700,0:25:41.400
Peace to My Ladies.

0:25:41.900,0:25:45.080
May I trouble you to inform Her Majesty
that Companion An and I request an audience?

0:25:45.200,0:25:46.880
You've come at an inopportune time, My Ladies.

0:25:47.000,0:25:48.360
Her Majesty is not here.

0:25:48.626,0:25:51.566
If I recall correctly, this is the time Her Majesty rises from her afternoon nap.

0:25:51.840,0:25:54.400
Her Majesty went to see His Majesty
 at the Governance Hall.

0:25:55.026,0:25:59.147
My Ladies, I believe Her Majesty and you have
endured today's scorching heat for the same reason.

0:26:00.020,0:26:01.860
Her Majesty is resourceful.

0:26:02.124,0:26:05.544
She anticipated our request and
 went to see His Majesty first.

0:26:05.741,0:26:08.020
It is uncertain when Her Majesty will be back.

0:26:08.226,0:26:10.340
Would you mind waiting in the side chamber?

0:26:10.500,0:26:12.540
Tea has been prepared.

0:26:12.540,0:26:14.180
Thank you, Madam Autumn.

0:26:14.400,0:26:15.318
Please.

0:26:19.500,0:26:21.180
The Empress went to the Governance Hall?

0:26:23.720,0:26:27.109
What for, in the midday heat?

0:26:28.220,0:26:32.680
I learned that Her Majesty was pleading
in favor of An Bihuai, Companion An's father.

0:26:35.000,0:26:38.880
You mean, the official who failed to escort the army provisions?

0:26:39.620,0:26:42.940
Your Highness's brother, General Nian,
is fighting valiantly on the frontier

0:26:43.204,0:26:46.285
while they couldn't do such
a small thing for him at the back end.

0:26:46.734,0:26:48.654
No wonder His Majesty was enraged.

0:26:50.220,0:26:51.540
Only ...

0:26:52.000,0:26:58.000
Is Your Highness going to pay a visit as well
now that the Empress has done Companion An a favor?

0:27:00.502,0:27:03.560
Isn't Companion An very close to Lady Sourire and Lady Vertu?

0:27:04.200,0:27:05.660
They are like sisters.

0:27:07.640,0:27:10.360
No one can be like sisters in the harem.

0:27:11.000,0:27:14.900
It's just the weak being reliant on the strong,
and the unintelligent obedient to the wise.

0:27:15.980,0:27:18.923
Sisters of today will become tomorrow's nemeses.

0:27:19.413,0:27:23.180
A smile on the face is only to hide a dagger in the back.

0:27:25.056,0:27:27.764
Your Highness's sharp words "draw blood with one needle."

0:27:29.580,0:27:35.460
Do you prefer the harem to be managed
with a velvet glove or an iron fist?

0:27:37.753,0:27:40.576
My dull-witted mind knows nothing of such things.

0:27:42.758,0:27:45.618
Conflicts occur wherever women gather.

0:27:46.940,0:27:51.700
They cry with scheming tears
and smile despite a spiteful mind.

0:27:52.859,0:27:57.760
The harem appears as a pond of still water,
but beneath the surface, turbulent currents surge.

0:27:59.840,0:28:04.320
Were I to govern the harem,
I would rule with an iron fist and iron heart.

0:28:05.761,0:28:10.000
I dare anyone to ignore law and discipline
under the threat of severe punishment.

0:28:10.704,0:28:12.387
Your Highness is absolutely right.

0:28:14.216,0:28:16.656
Her Majesty the Empress returns.

0:28:23.700,0:28:26.140
Peace and grace to Your Majesty.

0:28:26.300,0:28:27.700
All rise.

0:28:33.061,0:28:34.141
Have a seat.

0:28:34.480,0:28:35.880
I thank Your Majesty.

0:28:38.278,0:28:42.758
I did all I could to help Companion An's father.

0:28:43.060,0:28:44.600
But it isn't up to me.

0:28:45.302,0:28:50.002
His Majesty only said that it was a matter in court.

0:28:50.794,0:28:54.954
If Your Majesty says so ...
That is all I can do as well.

0:28:56.613,0:29:01.480
At this point, we can only count on Heaven's blessings,

0:29:01.800,0:29:07.440
and whether His Majesty will be open to further discussion.

0:29:13.000,0:29:15.760
Lingrong is most grateful for
Your Majesty's help and consideration.

0:29:16.137,0:29:19.157
I will always remember Your Majesty's benevolence.

0:29:20.000,0:29:21.161
You may rise.

0:29:22.600,0:29:25.060
Misfortune can befall anyone.

0:29:25.764,0:29:32.200
I am not only the head of the harem,
but also a sister to all of you in the family.

0:29:32.700,0:29:36.340
I must help you whenever my ability allows.

0:29:39.500,0:29:45.060
No matter how things turn out,
we are eternally grateful for Your Majesty's words.

0:29:46.500,0:29:50.820
Ever since I entered the palace, I have been intimidated
by Consort Fleur's cold and domineering eyes.

0:29:51.302,0:29:55.360
Your Majesty is a caring, motherly presence
to the harem and the whole nation.

0:29:56.726,0:29:57.980
I ...

0:29:59.321,0:30:05.261
Lady Sourire, you are a sensible person.
You must offer some comfort to Companion An.

0:30:06.120,0:30:09.180
I share the same gratitude as Companion An
for Your Majesty's care and support.

0:30:09.790,0:30:12.690
How may we possibly repay Your Majesty's favor?

0:30:14.500,0:30:19.800
There is one trouble after another in the harem, 
but my health limits my energy to manage it all.

0:30:20.800,0:30:28.460
With a perceptive mind like yours, Lady Sourire,
you can ease some of my worries, if you know what they are.

0:30:37.000,0:30:38.400
Aiya,

0:30:38.480,0:30:43.460
on such a hot day, the ash in the censer 
could flame back up.

0:30:43.686,0:30:45.646
What should we do about it?

0:31:06.980,0:31:10.200
It is by the grace of Your Majesty
that we can have a peaceful life in the palace.

0:31:10.660,0:31:14.460
We therefore must share Your Majesty's burdens.

0:31:14.826,0:31:17.342
"While the wise exercises their mind,"
we humble concubines

0:31:17.342,0:31:20.441
will take the necessary actions 
to return Your Majesty's kindness.

0:31:21.100,0:31:25.100
Very well, you did not let me down.

0:31:28.002,0:31:31.080
"Under the bright moon and faint stars,
fly the crows to the south afar."

0:31:31.080,0:31:34.000
"They encircle a tree for many a time,
finally able to rest upon a branch."

0:31:34.000,0:31:36.000
[Duan Ge Xing by Cao Cao]

0:31:36.460,0:31:40.440
In sooth, there is only one tree in the harem.

0:31:41.180,0:31:44.000
But the bright-colored flowers may deceive your eyes.

0:31:44.500,0:31:50.260
All is well as long as you can distinguish the tree from the flowers.

0:31:50.449,0:31:53.689
I thank Your Majesty.
I will always remember your advice.

0:31:59.520,0:32:04.240
Consort Fleur is aware that the Empress
has seen His Majesty for An Bihuai's case.

0:32:05.200,0:32:08.920
Right now, no one is more concerned about
Her Majesty than Consort Fleur.

0:32:09.615,0:32:13.120
Take a guess what Consort Fleur is doing.

0:32:13.200,0:32:16.220
Presumably, she is doing
the opposite of what Her Majesty did -

0:32:16.720,0:32:19.460
pleading with His Majesty to punish An Bihuai severely.

0:32:19.500,0:32:21.860
We must thank her if that's the case.

0:32:23.206,0:32:25.180
How so, My Lady?

0:32:25.804,0:32:32.064
We must thank her for putting in so much effort,
which will save us a lot of trouble.

0:33:10.000,0:33:13.480
When did you come in? I wasn't even aware.

0:33:14.002,0:33:16.820
Si Lang, you were soundly asleep.
I didn't have the heart to disturb you.

0:33:17.000,0:33:19.045
The memorandums are never exhausted before I am.

0:33:19.460,0:33:23.100
Before I know it, I have spent the entire day reading.

0:33:23.402,0:33:28.800
Those old fogeys never miss a day -
writing to bother me, even over nothing.

0:33:29.089,0:33:32.665
It is their duty as the officials.
Si Lang need not be too tough on them.

0:33:34.300,0:33:41.180
And with the affectionate ladies visiting to keep you company,
they must have made your work more enjoyable.

0:33:42.028,0:33:47.188
It must have been a poetic scene where a
"fragrant red cuff perfumed each turned page."

0:33:50.718,0:33:52.198
Hmm, it smells really good.

0:33:52.720,0:33:57.380
I've humored your cheeky tongue. 
You've grown even brasher.

0:33:58.800,0:34:02.321
Compared to Her Highness Consort Fleur,
Huan Huan barely understands Your Majesty.

0:34:03.000,0:34:05.236
All I do is upset Si Lang.

0:34:13.060,0:34:15.640
How did you know Consort Fleur was here?

0:34:18.340,0:34:21.345
The fan is scented with "Celestial Palace,"

0:34:21.900,0:34:25.400
a rare rouge that is intricately crafted
 with a captivating fragrance.

0:34:25.900,0:34:28.040
It's granted to very few in the palace.

0:34:29.180,0:34:31.600
Her Majesty eschews perfume,

0:34:31.760,0:34:36.060
so it must be Her Highness who came
elegantly dressed to see Your Majesty.

0:34:36.326,0:34:39.832
And the scent of her rouge lingers on the fan.

0:34:41.476,0:34:43.536
You can "discern a great truth from a small phenomenon."

0:34:43.980,0:34:45.640
Si Lang, just tell me if I'm right.

0:34:46.064,0:34:47.537
Your nose sees everything.

0:34:49.260,0:34:52.620
Consort Fleur set her foot in when the Empress had just left.

0:34:53.000,0:34:54.836
They came here for the same person.

0:34:55.539,0:34:58.740
Was it for Companion's father, An Bihuai?

0:34:58.900,0:35:00.000
Exactly.

0:35:00.800,0:35:04.372
What about you?
What brought you here?

0:35:05.600,0:35:07.482
Let Huan Huan take a guess.

0:35:08.620,0:35:12.434
Her Majesty is kind-hearted.
She must be pleading for Companion An.

0:35:13.089,0:35:19.100
Her Highness has a just mind.
She must be in favor of impersonal law enforcement.

0:35:19.220,0:35:20.541
What about you?

0:35:20.711,0:35:23.911
The harem must not interfere in state affairs.
Huan Huan always bears that in mind.

0:35:24.464,0:35:30.200
I'm just curious, since Her Majesty and Her Highness
had opposing views on the same issue,

0:35:30.704,0:35:36.600
does that mean their opinions can be reconciled
and the case is worth further examination?

0:35:37.215,0:35:38.917
What do you mean?

0:35:44.700,0:35:51.800
From my reading of history, the illustrious emperors
tended to punish the primary culprit while showing mercy to the dependents.

0:35:51.900,0:35:55.160
This would inspire in the people
not only reverence but also gratitude.

0:35:55.502,0:35:58.060
As an admirer of the founding emperors
of the Tang and Song Dynasties,

0:35:58.437,0:36:00.957
Your Majesty is a sagacious and benevolent emperor as well.

0:36:01.302,0:36:03.000
In my humble opinion,

0:36:03.226,0:36:08.366
the reign is bright when outward wars
and inward penalties are clear.

0:36:10.264,0:36:14.504
I have known you are well-versed in literature,

0:36:15.000,0:36:18.123
but you are also proficient in history and national tactics.

0:36:19.300,0:36:25.020
You inform governance in light of history
without direct reference to the state affairs.

0:36:25.364,0:36:28.946
I'm grateful to have your assistance,
as if adding a jewel to my crown.

0:36:31.260,0:36:36.474
I will have An Bihuai's case re-investigated.
No innocent should be unjustly convicted.

0:36:37.920,0:36:43.700
I hope Your Majesty will pardon
my brazen violation of the rules for women.

0:36:43.900,0:36:46.100
While the harem cannot interfere in the court,

0:36:46.389,0:36:51.279
I am your husband, not your monarch,
when you are alone with me.

0:36:52.580,0:36:56.680
From history to political views, you can speak
freely of anything with your husband.

0:36:56.700,0:36:58.800
There's nothing wrong with that.

0:36:59.206,0:37:00.414
I dare not.

0:37:00.414,0:37:04.733
Noble Lady Sourire doesn't dare to,
but Zhen Huan can.

0:37:10.923,0:37:15.592
Yes, I dare not overstep my bounds before Your Majesty,

0:37:16.573,0:37:20.160
but Huan Huan will talk her heart out to Si Lang.

0:37:28.302,0:37:30.820
I'm here to congratulate My Lady!

0:37:31.000,0:37:33.140
Thank you, Madam. What happened?

0:37:33.200,0:37:38.500
Early this morning, His Majesty ordered Shen Zishan,
the Commander of Jizhou to re-investigate your father's case.

0:37:38.640,0:37:40.515
We are hopeful that he will be spared.

0:37:41.962,0:37:43.040
Really?

0:37:43.040,0:37:44.080
Of course.

0:37:44.120,0:37:49.000
The Empress pleaded for the case yesterday, and
His Majesty must give face to Her Majesty.

0:37:50.000,0:37:51.461
I thank Her Majesty.

0:37:52.226,0:37:56.920
Not now, My Lady. You should thank Her Majesty
in person when all is well with your father.

0:37:57.420,0:38:01.198
It seems that Lady Sourire went to see His Majesty as well.

0:38:01.640,0:38:05.960
Lady Vertu and Lady Sourire are like sisters to you, My Lady!

0:38:06.514,0:38:09.474
Sourire does treat me wholeheartedly

0:38:10.000,0:38:11.396
while Meizhuang ...

0:38:11.861,0:38:16.148
Lady Vertu has sent a letter to Mr. Shen
to take care of the matter.

0:38:16.700,0:38:20.654
Anyone can give a push to the boat
when it's already carried by the current.

0:38:20.900,0:38:26.040
In fact, His Majesty was certainly going to
pardon Mr. An as the Empress spoke for you.

0:38:26.300,0:38:32.434
If only Lady Vertu had sent the letter sooner,
you wouldn't have to worry so much, My Lady.

0:38:34.677,0:38:37.600
I have some errands to run.
Please allow me to take my leave, My Lady.

0:38:37.700,0:38:39.092
Take care, Madam.

0:38:54.000,0:38:55.907
Coua...

0:38:56.436,0:38:59.376
Quickly, collect some valuable jewelry of mine.

0:38:59.640,0:39:04.758
My family must have spent a lot of money to buy favors from others.

0:39:05.600,0:39:09.376
