You can gain favor for yourself to "smooth
your furrowed eyebrows" and make your parents proud.

0:40:14.026,0:40:19.053
I'm incapable of that, and devoid of a chance to do so.

0:40:19.327,0:40:22.527
As long as you have the heart, My Lady,
there will be a way.

0:40:37.000,0:40:39.551
Why are you not fanning My Lady inside
when it's so hot right now?

0:40:39.740,0:40:42.229
His Majesty is here. I don't dare to stay in.

0:40:42.400,0:40:46.460
I'm using a sticky pole to catch the cicadas
so My Lady can have better sleep.

0:40:46.864,0:40:48.540
Only catching the cicadas on this tree?

0:40:48.540,0:40:51.980
There are many more trees in the outer yard.
It won't be quiet until you catch them all.

0:40:52.226,0:40:54.533
Hey, aren't you going to do it with me!

0:40:55.226,0:40:58.620
My Lady sent me to collect some lotus flowers
so she could see them after her nap.

0:40:58.620,0:41:00.140
I'm going to put them in a vase.

0:41:08.274,0:41:11.149
I beg Your Majesty's pardon.
I didn't know Your Majesty was here.

0:41:11.149,0:41:12.659
I didn't mean to interrupt.

0:41:13.300,0:41:16.140
My Lady, I didn't mean to.

0:41:18.000,0:41:21.580
You must be the Jade who likes to wear jade.

0:41:22.400,0:41:24.960
Yes, Your Majesty has a good memory.

0:41:28.880,0:41:30.805
You may leave after you put away the flowers.

0:41:31.220,0:41:32.161
Yes.

0:41:50.060,0:41:52.390
Why did you put the flowers in a big bowl?

0:41:53.640,0:41:58.737
Your Majesty, I was hoping to keep them floating
in the bowl the same way they're blooming on the lake.

0:41:58.737,0:42:00.737
They will look more beautiful.

0:42:02.240,0:42:05.558
You have a pretty face and an even more beautiful mind.

0:42:05.860,0:42:07.480
I thank Your Majesty.

0:42:16.126,0:42:18.108
Even your maid takes after you.

